channel.description:

item.title: Need MysticPk client or related/compatible
item.dc:creator: @ohokay ohokay
item.description:
@ohokay wrote:

[quote=“Camballer, post:4, topic:478662”][quote author=luna-scape link=topic=596887.msg4203054#msg4203054 date=1358509251]
Huh? It doesnt really matter what client you use?
Just fill in the ip> 127.0.0.1
Then it should work. Or use an ip changer…
Anyways provide some more information.
[/quote] You’re honestly not helpful whatsoever and your advice is misleading. It DOES matter which client he uses.

[quote author=ohokay link=topic=596887.msg4203055#msg4203055 date=1358509369]
wat.

Just download a decent source that has a client with it. Drop mysticpkz or whatever that is, sounds bad anyway.
[/quote] When someone asks for help, you help them with their problem. You don’t lead them to start a new project and forget it.

[quote author=end1snear link=topic=596887.msg4203037#msg4203037 date=1358503692]
i have MysticPk server files but i cant find a compatible client.if you have it or know where to get it please.
Thanks in advance!
+
there was a online client equivelant to moparisthebest.com

i know it’s "something"scape.org
[/quote] What’s the revision / base?[/quote]

If he doesn’t even have a client for the source he wants, I highly doubt it’s a project. In which case he can just download a better source and client which will provide him with a better base.

I believe I was helping.
